{
  "chapter": 39,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十九回\"丐帮英烈\"分为两条叙事线。前半章，辛捷为护方少魌和中原武林，独自硬接恒河三佛之首金伯胜夷的全力一掌，伤重倒地但未移动一步，完成使命。场景切换至洛阳城郊，丐帮护法金老大带着年幼帮主鹏儿藏身古庙，告知鹏儿将送他去边塞大侠风柏杨处习武。忽闻金老二遇敌，金老大让鹏儿东逃，自己赶往救援。鹏儿途中偶遇吴凌风，求其相助。吴凌风赶至林中，发现赤阳道人率四名弟子围攻金老大，乃杀父仇人。吴凌风先败三名弟子，后与赤阳道人激斗近百招，以\"断魂剑法\"险胜，却因天性善良临门犹豫，未能杀死赤阳。二人寻到金老二时，发现他已被武当道士暗算身亡。金老大仰天长笑后痛哭，最终抱起金老二遗体，携鹏儿离去。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_fang_shao_qi",
      "text": "魌妹！快走吧！别令我有牵挂！这蛮子的一掌我还受得了，只恐他不守信，则你们要逃也来不及了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "金叔叔，你要不要看看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "金叔叔，我们现在先找一个地方隐藏起来，好好把武功练强，再去报仇好么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金叔叔",
      "listener": "char_peng_er",
      "text": "鹏儿，我有一件事，一直想跟你说，现在你既然想要练武报仇，正合我的计划。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "什么计划？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金叔叔",
      "listener": "char_peng_er",
      "text": "咱们丐帮，目下零落四散，是步步衰落了。可是丐帮弟子中，忠义之士大不乏人，只要一朝帮主振臂一呼，重新恢复从前盛况，那也是不太难的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "金叔叔，你是要我就去号召天下丐帮弟子，重振帮威吗？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金叔叔",
      "listener": "char_peng_er",
      "text": "现在你年纪这么小，武功又没有练成，要想统率这天下第一大帮，那是万万不能的，我的意思是先把你送到我一个好朋友边塞大侠风柏杨家里去，苦练几年武功。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "金叔叔，那么你呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金叔叔",
      "listener": "char_peng_er",
      "text": "我们丐帮的规矩，老帮主一死，他所聘的护法，便算解除职务了。我和老二，自然不能例外。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "金叔叔我不要离开你，我不要到什么边塞大侠家去，你……你教鹏儿的武功不可以吗？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金叔叔",
      "listener": "char_peng_er",
      "text": "傻孩子，那风大侠武功高我十倍不止，你到那儿去，最多五年，不但老帮主传的功夫可以练成，而且风大侠独立一派的关外武功也可以学得，岂不胜过跟着叔叔到处流浪吗？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "金叔叔，鹏儿作错了什么事吗，您……您为什么不再管鹏儿了？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金叔叔",
      "listener": "char_peng_er",
      "text": "鹏儿，老二遇着强敌了，你……你赶快向东逃走，这里的事，由我来打发，如果……如果，我金老大能侥幸活着，我自会到洛阳寻你，鹏儿，记着，如果等我们三天不来，你一个人到辽东锦州去找风大侠，就说是我叫你去的。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金叔叔",
      "listener": "char_peng_er",
      "text": "鹏儿，你今后可要更加小心了，你金叔叔也许……也许，不再有机会来保护你啦。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "金叔叔，你赶快去帮二叔叔吧！鹏儿在洛阳等你。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_peng_er",
      "text": "小弟，你走路真不留心呀，差一点就撞着我。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "我心中正在想事，所以不知自己正走在路中间。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_peng_er",
      "text": "小弟，你有什么心事，告诉我，我一定替你想法解决。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "我两位金叔叔被坏人攻击，情势很是危险，你可不可以去帮忙打一架？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_peng_er",
      "text": "你两位金叔叔在哪里和坏人打呀？你金叔叔叫什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "我金叔叔就是丐帮护法金老大、金老二……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_peng_er",
      "text": "快！快，你赶快带我去。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "你赶快去帮我金大叔，我要去寻找二叔。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_yang",
      "speaker_name": "年老道士",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "金老大，快把剑鞘交来，否则，哼，贫道可要不客气了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_yang",
      "speaker_name": "年老道士",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "金老大，你还敢倔强吗？此刻你们丐帮帮主已落在我弟子手中了，你以为那小帮主逃得到洛阳吗？哈哈贫道老早派人在路上恭候了。你如不献出剑鞘，嘿嘿……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_chi_yang",
      "text": "赤阳……赤阳贼道；真威风啊！以众欺寡，好神气啊！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_yang",
      "speaker_name": "赤阳道人",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "好，吴小子，又碰着你啦，咱们正好了结一下。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_chi_yang",
      "text": "你们武当派是惯于以多击少的，一起上来吧。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_yang",
      "speaker_name": "赤阳道人",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "小子，你别卖狂，你如能打败我三个徒儿，道爷便放你走路。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_yang",
      "speaker_name": "赤阳道人",
      "listener": "char_yi_he",
      "text": "一鹤，把我这支剑拿去，好好与这小子较量较量，莫要折了武当威名。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_yi_he",
      "text": "请上吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "金叔叔，您怎么啦？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_peng_er",
      "text": "鹏儿，我叫你走，怎的不听我话。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "金叔叔，我不要离开你，我要和你死在一块儿。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_peng_er",
      "text": "鹏儿，别哭啦，金叔叔答应不再离开你了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "金叔叔，他一定会打赢的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "金叔叔，你看我说得对不对？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_peng_er",
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "我早说他能把这些臭道士全部打跑。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_chi_yang",
      "text": "赤阳贼道，你打不赢他的，大伙儿一起上啊！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_yang",
      "speaker_name": "赤阳道人",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "贼叫化，你替我安静，宰这小子，何须别人相助。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_chi_yang",
      "text": "赤阳贼道，休逞口舌之利，今日便叫你归天。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "你可觉得哪儿不舒服？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_peng_er",
      "text": "小弟，你放心，那贼道怎能伤我？倒是你金叔叔，内力消耗过度，我这儿有瓶灵泉，可以助他赶快恢复哩。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "请教阁下大名。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "晚辈吴凌风。这是万年温玉所孕灵泉，功效非常神妙，老前辈先服一滴再说。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "吴大侠，你替咱们丐帮抵挡强仇，保护咱们小帮主，此恩此德，丐帮全体弟子不敢稍忘，如有吩咐，水里火里，无不从命。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "金老前辈，您快别这样，晚辈有个拜弟名叫辛捷，常向晚辈提及老前辈的英风高义，晚辈心中真是仰慕得很。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "原来吴大侠是辛老弟的义兄，难怪这好武功，那么老叫化托个大，也喊你一声老弟吧。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "丐帮怎也会和武当结仇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "这事说来话长，现在先寻老二吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹏儿",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_er",
      "text": "金二叔，鹏儿来啦！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_peng_er",
      "text": "鹏儿，你金二叔已死了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    }
  ],
  "new_entities": {
    "characters": [
